Package com.esri.mo2.data.omc

Supports caching of objects.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Cacheable This interface implements a Selectable Dataset that can be registered with com.esri.mo2.data.omc.Cache.
RemoteFeatureClass This interface implements a client FeatureClass associated with a FeatureClass residing on a remote server.
RemoteQuery Defines additional data for a RemoteFeatureClass when it is queried by the TileCache.
 

Class Summary
Cache This class implements a static object that serves as the cache for all Cacheable/Identifiable objects in an application.
ScaleDataID Implementation of the DataID interface that also allows a scale factor to be stored.
TileCache A Tile Cache is a Collection of visited Tiles (Areas), where each tile has a collection of visited RemoteFeatureClass.
